        <abstract>
            <p>CD obliged for JMH’s labours in "the science". He reports having spent a pleasant month. Entomological pursuits succeeded.</p>
            <p>Looks forward to receiving beetles and butterflies from JMH when he passes through Shrewsbury.</p>
        </abstract>
